node.text: Happy Parents' Day! After all you’ve done for us, being your on-call tech support is the least we can do. How do you plan to celebrate your parents today? Comment below 👇

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by UScellular on May 09, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'YES Do you know who you're celebrating today? NO'.

node.text:
This #MothersDay, all signs point ​
to “call your mom!” (No really — give her a call. Or a text, video chat, landline, courier pigeon, message in a bottle... you catch our drift).

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by UScellular on May 09, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'YES Do you know who you're celebrating today? NO'.
Photo by UScellular on May 09, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'Do you have a phone? DUH Hint: She may or may not have birthed you/raised you/ changed your diapers. oH!'.
Photo by UScellular on May 09, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'Have you called her today? YES NO Ding Ding Ding! Know what that rhymes with? Maybe?'.

Photo by UScellular on May 09, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'Congrats, you're probably the favorite child. Pull up her contact, we'll wait. Ring Ring Ring! (A.K.A. what you should give her today)'.
